     5‚Üí# Breaking changes
     6‚Üí
     7‚Üí## TypeScript v5
     8‚Üí
     9‚ÜíBecause it relies on [const type parameters](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/release-notes/typescript-5-0.html#const-type-parameters), TS-Pattern v5 requires TypeScript v5+!
    10‚Üí
    11‚Üí## `.with` is now evaluated eagerly
    12‚Üí
